        <p class="muted">This sample page demonstrates typical cost categories families might face during diagnosis and treatment journeys for rare diseases. The figures shown are illustrative only and not medical or financial advice.</p>

        <h3 style="margin-top:1rem">What this covers</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>One-time costs: diagnostics, surgery, initial hospitalization</li>
          <li>Recurring medical costs: specialized medications, infusions, monitoring</li>
          <li>Indirect costs: travel, lodging, lost wages, home modifications</li>
        </ul>

        <div style="margin-top:1rem">
          <div class="section-title">
            <h2>Estimated total (fictional)</h2>
            <div class="muted">First year estimate</div>
