        <h3>Detailed cost breakdown</h3>
        <table aria-describedby="cost-table">
          <thead>
            <tr><th>Category</th><th class="muted">Notes</th><th style="width:120px">Estimated cost</th></tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr><td>Diagnostic testing & genetic sequencing</td><td class="muted">Advanced labs, panels</td><td class="amount">$8,500</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Specialist consultations & second opinions</td><td class="muted">Multiple visits, telehealth</td><td class="amount">$4,200</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Initial hospitalization & surgery (if required)</td><td class="muted">Operating room and inpatient stay</td><td class="amount">$48,000</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Specialized medication / biologics</td><td class="muted">Often ongoing; cost varies widely</td><td class="amount">$290,000 / year</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Outpatient infusions & clinic visits</td><td class="muted">Nursing, infusion center fees</td><td class="amount">$18,000</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Travel & lodging</td><td class="muted">Regional specialist visits, caretakers</td><td class="amount">$10,000</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Home modifications & medical equipment</td><td class="muted">Ramp, hospital bed, durable equipment</td><td class="amount">$7,800</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Lost income / caregiving</td><td class="muted">Estimated reduced household earnings</td><td class="amount">$3,000</td></tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <p class="small" style="margin-top:.75rem">Note: recurring medication figures are annualized and will vary depending on country, insurance coverage, and manufacturer assistance programs.</p>

        <hr style="margin:1rem 0;border:none;border-top:1px solid #eef2f7" />

        <h3>How families typically cope</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Insurance appeals and prior authorization requests</li>
          <li>Manufacturer patient-assistance & co-pay relief</li>
          <li>Community fundraising (crowdfunding, events)</li>
          <li>Grants from rare-disease foundations</li>
        </ul>

